  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship Exhaust Modifier</span>.<br><br>A ramshackle ship exhaust nozzle, hand-assembled in an emergency by an outlaw. Has an occasional propensity to explode, but with no adverse effect on flight handling.<br><br>Install this <span class=\"name name-technology\">technology</span> in your starship inventory to change the appearance of the engine exhaust trails.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船排气管修改器</span>。<br><br>一个破旧的飞船排气管，由一名亡命之徒在紧急情况下手工组装而成。偶尔会有爆炸的倾向，但对飞行操作没有不利影响。<br><br>在你的飞船库存中安装这个<span class=\"name name-technology\">技术</span>可改变驱动器排气管尾迹的外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船排氣管改造器</span>。<br><br>搖搖欲墜的噴嘴，由亡命之徒在緊急時手工組裝而成。偶爾會爆炸，但不會對飛行操縱性造成不良影響。<br><br>安裝此<span class=\"name name-technology\">科技</span>到你的太空船道具欄，改變引擎廢氣尾跡的外觀。"
  },
